From: meta-nxp-mr <nxp@example.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] common: add sys/stat.h include for GCC15 compatibility

GCC15 (paired with glibc 2.39) no longer allows implicit availability of
stat() via transitive includes. Add an explicit #include <sys/stat.h> to
gst_pipeline_imx.cpp which uses struct stat and the stat() syscall wrapper.

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: meta-nxp-mr <nxp@example.com>
---
 common/cpp/src/gst_pipeline_imx.cpp | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/common/cpp/src/gst_pipeline_imx.cpp b/common/cpp/src/gst_pipeline_imx.cpp
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/common/cpp/src/gst_pipeline_imx.cpp
+++ b/common/cpp/src/gst_pipeline_imx.cpp
@@ -6,6 +6,7 @@
 #include "gst_pipeline_imx.hpp"
 #include <cmath>
 #include <regex>
+#include <sys/stat.h>
 
 
 // Default font size is 15 pixels for a width of 640
